@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
    <p>Learn about this project</p>
    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Products</h2>
            <p>The Products section allows you to manage the list of products available in the inventory. You can add
                new products, update existing product details, and delete products that are no longer available. This
                section ensures that the product catalog is always up-to-date.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Sales</h2>
            <p>The Sales section provides functionality to record and manage sales transactions. You can create new
                sales records, view past sales, and generate sales reports. This section helps in tracking revenue and
                understanding sales trends over time.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Inventory</h2>
            <p>The Inventory section is crucial for maintaining the stock levels of products. You can view current
                inventory levels, update quantities, and monitor stock movements. This section ensures that you have
                accurate and real-time information about product availability.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Purchases</h2>
            <p>The Purchases section allows you to manage procurement activities. You can record new purchases, update
                purchase orders, and track supplier information. This section helps in maintaining a smooth supply chain
                and ensuring that inventory levels are replenished as needed.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>
